        "jsCode": "const leads = $input.first().json.data || [];  // 如果 data 是 undefined，则赋值为一个空数组\nconst name = $('Get contact ID by Mobile').first().json.Full_Name; \n\nconst filteredLeads = leads.filter(lead => lead.Full_Name === name);\n\nreturn filteredLeads.map(lead => ({ json: lead }));"
